Up for sale is my Mossberg 464 Lever Action .22!  My wife and I purchased this rifle about 5 months ago and loved shooting with it.  Unfortunately we will be moving in the next few months, and the money for the move is more important than shooting for us at the moment, so it's time to downsize. 
 
This rifle is perfect for someone looking for a plinker, target shooting, cowboy action, or just about anything you could want from a .22!  It's rugged, it's got a nice smooth action, it feels well built, and it shoots straighter than I can.  It's practically new-in-box.
